Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.44,0:00:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.34,0:00:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.74,0:00:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.94,0:00:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.34,0:00:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.34,0:00:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.34,0:01:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.34,0:01:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.88,0:01:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.00,0:01:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙,那是人类第2个故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.24,0:01:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当地球无法负荷增加过多人口时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.32,0:01:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们在宇宙制造新的大地与城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.88,0:02:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从第一个大型殖民地可供4千万人生活时候起,\N宇宙世纪就开启了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一话 前奏曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这各巨大圆桶的自转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.44,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使内侧墙壁的大地,产生人工重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.28,0:02:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3个具大镜子,将阳光收到殖民地内部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制造出森林与湖泊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.07,0:02:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里,气象也是人工控制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.07,0:02:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样具大的建筑物\N是在强化宇宙服与
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.17,0:02:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作业用机器人开发后才得以建设出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.93,0:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而这个作业用机器人,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还发展成战斗用机器人MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS是宇宙世纪产生的终极机动武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.95,0:03:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于米诺夫基粒子的被发现使雷达无用武之地的这个时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可进行格斗战的MS,成了最强的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.46,0:03:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后在知道那战斗能力\N足可与宇宙巡洋舰匹敌之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.96,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们开始燃起战争的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.79,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.55,0:03:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开发最初的量产MS萨克\N的宇宙殖民地国家SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.41,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自称吉翁公国 对地球连邦宣布独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时代于是进入将地球与宇宙一分为二的混乱时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化悲伤为力量\N站起来吧,国民们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别忘记我们吉翁国公民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.19,0:04:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是被神选上的子民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有优良的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能拯救人类\N吉翁万岁！ 吉翁万岁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.62,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁万岁！ 吉翁万岁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地坠落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了彰显萨克威力的这个计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.74,0:04:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬间就夺走数千万人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗·雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.61,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶然间坐上联邦军\N最新锐MS高达的这位少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在多次作战中,成长成无敌的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一样的啊,是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害，能量是通常的5倍以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.72,0:05:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被称为白色MS的高达\N战斗力果然惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗觉醒成新人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.75,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时代称这是人类的革新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人类的革新并没有全部达成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类又开始再度战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[泰坦斯要塞.格林普斯2]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由军人精英组成,以管理地球本身为目标的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.31,0:06:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泰坦斯在贾米托夫·海曼手中创立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.35,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以其强大力量为背景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.17,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做比吉翁公国更坏的事业\N企图统治人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令一方面,为了抵抗泰坦斯成立了奥古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.79,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前自护的红色彗星夏亚·阿兹那布鲁也参与其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类脱离地球控制的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未何人类还要争战不休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,污染地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.89,0:06:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许人永远不可能觉醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前我们有阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我们有卡缪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.69,0:06:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这混沌的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,许多人们被巨大海浪吞没\N熄灭生命之火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.73,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚加玛奉命攻下格林普斯2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.74,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了治愈受伤的身心\N前往SIDE 1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往西航行0301
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我们打败了西洛克 击沉了朱庇特利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是代价也太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.59,0:07:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奥古的指导者夏亚·阿兹那布鲁没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪也情况不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身心都受到重创
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须早一些到达SIDE 1才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来在这里,花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心卡缪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.44,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1有好医生,提起精神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪，你还记得吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.39,0:08:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗达，冠武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.94,0:08:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我们经常吵架\N你总是那么温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要加入战斗的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊,花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是去看MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看自己的MS是哪一款吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗,\N你只是后补驾驶员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交给我就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是来支援的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你趁现在休息好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一场作战很快就开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪，可是你的心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！你怎么还要让这种事发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.22,0:09:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么意思？阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.69,0:09:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不赶快阻止他们俩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说那个叫做凤的女孩的事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想让同样的悲剧再度上演吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪 卡缪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.91,0:09:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到刚才我都想不起卡缪你了,\N这是为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为你讨厌我了对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我变了,当坐上精神力高达时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤？凤，你能跑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤…你…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁？是敌人对吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要杀死你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.83,0:10:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.82,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，打开驾驶舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡缪，是你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能再留在精神力高达的驾驶舱里了\N快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.68,0:10:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧，卡缪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一样吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！你觉悟吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.57,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.47,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人总是重复同样的错误,\N真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.27,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤，睁开眼睛吧，骗人的吧\N这是骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睁开眼睛啊，凤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.17,0:11:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间的泪水留不止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.33,0:11:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战火中消逝的人们的思念\N何时才能达成呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最新MS名录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一个问题，这台MS是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百式！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古华多罗·巴吉纳，百式出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.42,0:12:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌,你还装蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚，也就是说古华多罗上尉战斗经验都很丰富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.96,0:12:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗力高的百式 是本系列代表性的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.95,0:12:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第2个问题？这是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力奇·戴亚斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.46,0:12:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是奥古开发的高机动MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.06,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力奇.戴亚斯的力奇\N意思是指宇宙用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:13:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴亚斯是取自喜望锋的发现者巴斯罗谬·戴亚斯的姓氏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以叫力奇·戴亚斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.87,0:13:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说取这个名字是古华多罗上尉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人说使用高达合金的力奇·戴亚斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第2代MS的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是高达MK-Ⅱ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.30,0:13:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对,这是超级高达\N他装上了G防卫号的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.16,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然高达MK-Ⅱ是泰坦斯秘密开发的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因古华多罗与卡缪的活跃而成为了奥古的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要变形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,0085的MS的最大特征,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个变形MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.48,0:13:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像燕子一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.47,0:13:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸札上尉的汉布拉克\N是3机为一队的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是罗沙美亚姐姐的猎犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机器人迷当中,\N有人认为这是最美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.56,0:14:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高达MK-Ⅱ你的实力就只有这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,色子高达出现了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乱讲 这是精神力高达才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.67,0:14:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的体型巨大很让人惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了，看我的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡碧尼拥有应用了精神系统的浮游炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.23,0:14:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是用脑波控制的小型光束炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.50,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，最棒的MS当然是百式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.13,0:14:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那当然是Z高达最厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在是个倒楣人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.60,0:14:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高达加上卡缪·比丹的新人类能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.34,0:14:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确发挥超强的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲浪者形态也很帅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.39,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动作这么大，卡缪哥哥怎么都不会眼花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.34,0:15:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,最后是大家等候已久的 MS谜题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请将登场的MS名字与型号输入电子邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答对的人,可抽选招待到木星旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请寄到SIDE 6第23区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦,好啦,你们可别当真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到了SIDE 3的阿克西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.56,0:17:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是扎比家的正统继承者\N米涅芭·扎比公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.72,0:17:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用扎比家被忘记的继承者 米涅芭·扎比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且声称有复兴吉翁公国的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.30,0:17:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,各部队都准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令全体舰队发动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,哈曼大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.59,0:17:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1方面的军舰巴西马斯号,\N出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.25,0:17:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1的香格里拉殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.99,0:17:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香格里拉是最旧的宇宙殖民地\N因受到多次战火摧残而荒废
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.31,0:17:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连自转速度都控制失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.65,0:18:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个SIDE都是由40个左右的殖民卫星构成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.36,0:18:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个殖民地由1开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依序取了偏号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.26,0:18:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1到SIDE 7的宇宙都市\N是以太阳与月球与地球引力的中力点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.17,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉格朗日点为中心\N划出各自运转的轨道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集尖端科技而建造的宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有许多维持宇宙生活的设备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.96,0:18:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及许多安全系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.39,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是动画，是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是动画，是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.11,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，我是捷度·阿西塔\N住在SIDE 1香格里拉殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界真难混
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不出外工作就活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就当起收破烂的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.40,0:19:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的工作是捡回MS的废铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这工作很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.98,0:19:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,我有可爱的妹妹与\N重要的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.45,0:19:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子都是新人类\N表现给大人看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 队长是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚加玛来到香格里拉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.71,0:20:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是大赚一笔的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那上面有Z高达啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.26,0:20:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要偷到它\N我们就能告别这个殖民卫星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，一下子就得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.86,0:20:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捡回这怪人是一连串错误的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他叫逸札对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人要靠胆量，把Z高达抢过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.27,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果哥哥可以改掉这无拘无束的性格就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.06,0:20:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,累死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.26,0:20:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔！给我赚一笔吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好… 好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看看\N她也是亚加玛的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿嘿…不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.83,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是\N亚加玛有更厉害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是卡缪·比丹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那感觉究竟是什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.21,0:21:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是新人类吗？\N世界上真的有新人类吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之我们先把Z高达抢过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的以后再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是每个月都有买MS杂志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高达什么的我肯定能操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.99,0:21:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,你别忘恩负义，我是救你的人啊！\N这个混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我最讨厌大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.55,0:21:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.17,0:21:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你技术太嫩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.93,0:22:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？结果失败了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,我看不过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度和比查你们继续这样下去行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有怪东西接近了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.60,0:22:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚加玛追上来了\N为什么我也得被拖下水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.12,0:22:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是男子汉吧\N自己惹的祸自己收拾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！我要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.25,0:22:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人类要是害怕的话\N还能来驾驶Z高达吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.50,0:22:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.50,0:22:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.90,0:23:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.10,0:23:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.20,0:23:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.90,0:23:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いてい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.00,0:23:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1的殖民卫星是我们出生长大的殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对 我还正在长大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生存真是很艰难！
